          <iconify-icon icon="mdi:shield-lock" class="text-2xl text-primary"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-center md:text-left">Maximale beveiliging</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-center md:text-left">Imunify360, dagelijkse backups, gratis SSL en proactieve monitoring.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 mx-auto md:mx-0">
          <iconify-icon icon="mdi:scale" class="text-2xl text-primary"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-center md:text-left">Onbeperkt schalen</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-center md:text-left">Geen limieten op verkeer, databases of bezoekers – groei zonder zorgen.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 mx-auto md:mx-0">
          <iconify-icon icon="mdi:leaf" class="text-2xl text-green-600"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-center md:text-left">100% groen</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-center md:text-left">Hernieuwbare energie + boom-planting per nieuwe site.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 mx-auto md:mx-0">
          <iconify-icon icon="mdi:headset" class="text-2xl text-amber-600"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-center md:text-left">Prioriteit support</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-center md:text-left">Snelle Nederlandse hulp via chat, telefoon en ticket.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 mx-auto md:mx-0">
          <iconify-icon icon="mdi:clock-fast" class="text-2xl text-purple-600"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-center md:text-left">Direct live</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-center md:text-left">Binnen minuten actief – geen wachttijd.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
